  "prompt": "What kinds of flowers do girls like besides roses?",
  "response": "The choice of flowers can vary widely depending on individual preferences, but there are several types of flowers that are generally popular and well-liked:\n\n1. **Tulips** - Bright and cheerful, tulips come in a variety of colors and can symbolize different things from love to happiness.\n\n2. **Lilies** - Elegant and often fragrant, lilies are appreciated for their beauty and sophistication.\n\n3. **Daisies** - Simple and charming, daisies bring a sense of innocence and joy.\n\n4. **Orchids** - Exotic and unique, orchids are admired for their grace and intricate beauty.\n\n5. **Sunflowers** - Bold and vibrant, sunflowers can bring a sense of warmth and positivity.\n\n6. **Peonies** - Lush and full, peonies are loved for their romantic and luxurious appeal.\n\n7. **Carnations** - Versatile and long-lasting, carnations come in many colors and can symbolize admiration and love.\n\n8. **Irises** - Striking and elegant, irises often represent faith and hope.\n\n9. **Gardenias** - Known for their intoxicating fragrance, gardenias are a symbol of secret love.\n\n10. **Hydrangeas** - Beautiful clusters of petals in various colors, hydrangeas represent heartfelt emotions.\n\nRemember that personal preferences can be quite unique, so it's always a good idea to consider the individual tastes of the person you are buying flowers for.",
